B052C002V017	52	2	17	But we, brethren, being taken from you for a short time in presence, not in heart, endeavoured the more abundantly to see your face with great desire.
B052C002V018	52	2	18	Therefore we would have come to you, even I Paul, once and again; but Satan hindered us.
B052C002V019	52	2	19	For what 
