B052C005V019	52	5	19	Quench not the Spirit.
B052C005V020	52	5	20	Despise not prophesyings.
B052C005V021	52	5	21	Examine all things; hold fast that which is good.
B052C005V022	52	5	22	Abstain from all appearance of evil.
B052C005V023	52	5	23	And the very God of peace sanctify you wholly; and 
B052C005V024	52	5	24	Faithful 
