B062C002V009	62	2	9	He that saith he is in the light, and hateth his brother, is in darkness even until now.
B062C002V010	62	2	10	He that loveth his brother abideth in the light, and there is no cause for stumbling in him. 
B062C002V011	62	2	11	But he that hateth his brother is in darkness, and walketh in darkness, and knoweth not where he goeth, because that darkness hath blinded his eyes.
B062C002V012	62	2	12	I write to you, little children, because your sins are forgiven you for his name’s sake.
