B062C003V004	62	3	4	Whoever committeth sin transgresseth also the law: for sin is the transgression of the law.
B062C003V005	62	3	5	And ye know that he appeared to take away our sins; and in him is no sin.
B062C003V006	62	3	6	Whoever abideth in him sinneth not: whoever sinneth hath not seen him, neither known him.
B062C003V007	62	3	7	Little children, let no man deceive you: he that doeth righteousness is righteous, even as he is righteous.
