B062C003V024	62	3	24	And he that keepeth his commandments dwelleth in him, and he in him. And by this we know that he abideth in us, by the Spirit who he hath given to us.
B062C004V001	62	4	1	Beloved, believe not every spirit, but try the spirits whether they are of God: because many false prophets have gone out into the world.
B062C004V002	62	4	2	By this ye know the Spirit of God: Every spirit that confesseth that Jesus Christ hath come in the flesh is from God:
